{"title":"和平","authors":["安娜丽莎·卡索"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":12,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔意大利〕安娜丽莎·卡索"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（女中学生十五岁）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“和平”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"音调优美。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类的和平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宇宙的和平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"士兵的喜悦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲的拥抱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子脸上天真的笑容，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熙熙攘攘街道上年轻人的欢乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中的幸福。对明天的希望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个更美好的明天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个和平的明天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（杨顺祥译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}